org.hbase.async.auth
Class ClientAuthProvider

java.lang.Object
  org.hbase.async.auth.ClientAuthProvider
Direct Known Subclasses:
KerberosClientAuthProvider, SimpleClientAuthProvider
public abstract class ClientAuthProvider
extends Object

Class to extend to support other authentication mechanisms for Secure RPC versions. To select a provider fully qualified class names are passed to 'hbase.security.authentication' system property.

Since:
1.7
